# pricing — four arguments, four distinct kāraka roles. The call carries no
# commas, no parens, no `name=` labels: each role is a 1–2 char suffix, and
# order is free. This is where kāraka beats keyword arguments outright.
#   adhara (base) -m   kara (tax) -ena   chut (discount) -aya   sankhya (qty) -e
karya mulya(adharam, karaena, chutaya, sankhyae):
    phala (adhara + adhara * kara - chut) * sankhya

[100m 0.1ena 5aya 3e mulya]m vada
